[3255] Changes with nginx 1.1.17                                        15 Mar 2012
[3256] 
[3257]     *) Security: content of previously freed memory might be sent to a
[3258]        client if backend returned specially crafted response.
[3259]        Thanks to Matthew Daley.
[3260] 
